item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

Uhh. What?
By the way, you’re client isn’t a PI client. PI is a server.

So first you add the interface to your client. Then you replace the interface ID that is in your ClickingButton.java (or ActionButton.java) with the one you just made.
